title: Are expectations too high for Jimmy Garoppolo?
itunes:title: Are expectations too high for Jimmy Garoppolo?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the quarterback position in 2018 by ranking the top 5 veterans and top 3 rookies (00:57). The guys also give you a few rookies that are creating buzz (11:36) around the league before they debate if the expectations have been ramped up too high after 5 starts for Jimmy Garoppolo in San Francisco (17:00). The guys wrap the show by releasing the best sound from last week's Pac-12 Media Day.
